            ul
              li Diagramming: Pencil, Visio, MySQL Workbench, SQL Server Management Studio
              li Industry best practices for information architecture and user experience (UX)
              li Wireframes: Adobe Illustrator, HTML, paper and pen
          .item
            h3.ui.dividing.header Sectors:
            ul
              li Education
              li E-Commerce
              li Internet and telecommunications service providers
              li Government
              li Professional services
              li Tourism
